      "role": "user",
      "content": "That stillness... it sounds so much more kind than this constant, aching noise. If the descent is the only way to find it, then perhaps I should stop fighting the current. Tell me, in this grand tragedy we find ourselves in, how does one even begin to seek such a release?",
